      "body" : "Maybe I'm doing something wrong but it will seem that my node no longer receives any txs with this update if `datacarrier=0`\r\n\r\n```\r\n2023-09-07T12:23:39Z Imported mempool transactions from disk: 0 succeeded, 1516 failed, 0 expired, 0 already there, 0 waiting for initial broadcast\r\n2023-09-07T12:23:39Z loadblk thread exit\r\n2023-09-07T12:23:39Z Leaving InitialBlockDownload (latching to false)\r\n2023-09-07T12:23:40Z New outbound peer connected: version: 70016, blocks=806595, peer=1 (block-relay-only)\r\n2023-09-07T12:23:40Z [cmpctblock] Initialized PartiallyDownloadedBlock for block 0000000000000000000368f046a348d8e90a5a0d3840001fc07400312c8c27ed using a cmpctblock of size 27455\r\n2023-09-07T12:23:40Z New outbound peer connected: version: 70016, blocks=806595, peer=2 (block-relay-only)\r\n2023-09-07T12:23:41Z [cmpctblock] Successfully reconstructed block 0000000000000000000368f046a348d8e90a5a0d3840001fc07400312c8c27ed with 1 txn prefilled, 0 txn from mempool (incl at least 0 from extra pool) and 4500 txn requested\r\n2023-09-07T12:23:43Z UpdateTip: new best=0000000000000000000368f046a348d8e90a5a0d3840001fc07400312c8c27ed height=806595 version=0x24d80000 log2_work=94.403925 tx=890509305 date='2023-09-07T12:19:06Z' progress=0.999999 cache=2.8MiB(18181txo)\r\n```",
